        (8, N'Puss in Boots: The Last Wish', N'PG', 102, N'2D', N'English', N'2022-12-21', N'https://res.cloudinary.com/dewgvguem/image/upload/v1733310291/twish_uqwgmn.jpg', N'Tayang', N'Animation, Adventure, Comedy', N'Guillermo del Toro', N'Joel Crawford', N'https://www.youtube.com/embed/RqrXhwS33yc?si=KRl_DamaMmj-1Toh', N'The legendary Puss in Boots discovers that his reckless lifestyle has taken its toll, and he''s used up eight of his nine lives. To restore his lost lives, Puss embarks on an epic quest to find the mythical Wishing Star. Along the way, he teams up with a clever and resourceful Kitty Softpaws and a cynical yet endearing canine named Perrito. Together, they face dangerous adversaries and heartwarming challenges in a race against time to save Puss''s life and restore his legendary status. '),
